# Source list for the Nintendo Switch build (included by Makefile.switch).
#
# This mirrors the Linux CODE_SOURCES list, with two platform swaps:
#   src/osapi/os_unix.cpp     -> src/osapi/os_nx.cpp     (SDL2 + libnx OS layer)
#   src/freespace2/unixmain.cpp -> src/freespace2/nxmain.cpp (libnx entry point)
# and with src/graphics/eglport.cpp left out (SDL2 owns the GL context).

